          <strong style="display:block; margin-bottom: 4px;">Legal identity of the publisher</strong>
          <span style="color: var(--ink-soft);">Claude-Alain Martin · sole proprietorship (Switzerland) · not registered in the Commercial Register (<strong>art. 36 ORC</strong>, turnover &lt; 100,000 CHF) · not subject to VAT (<strong>art. 10 para. 2 LTVA</strong>) · legal venue <strong>Berne</strong> for TARES, Ogens (Publisher's location) for other datasets · contact: <a href="mailto:contact@openswissdata.com">contact@openswissdata.com</a></span>
