          <td class="px-3 py-2 align-top">Request sent 2026-04-17 · Awaiting FINMA reply</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
    </div>
    <p class="legal-meta" style="margin: 8px 0; padding: 0; border: none;">
      Source files are downloaded from the public portals of the issuing authorities, hashed in SHA-256, normalised (stable schema, multilingual FR/DE/IT/EN, NACE/ISIC cross-walks), versioned and Ed25519-signed. For technical details: <a href="/legal/provenance" class="text-indigo-600 hover:underline">/legal/provenance</a>.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-10 mb-3">2. Pending permission requests</h2>
